Follow up from the LSD paper: new simulations to use different models of rate heterogeneity other than the lognormal they used.

Their webpage: http://www.atgc-montpellier.fr/LSD/

The true trees were downloaded from http://www.atgc-montpellier.fr/download/datasets/LSD/simulation/TrueUnrootedTreesWithDates.tar.gz
